location.fullValue: McCormick II Plan, Gregory Pointe at Deercreek

data.description: This beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 and half bath house is located just outside the city limits of Manning in a well established neighborhood. The house has 9 foot ceilings, screened in back porch with a large outside porch. House also has a double garage with an handicapped accessible elevator if needed or can be removed. The outside has a large Concrete pad with electricity for a RV or similar vehicle and two storage sheds one with electricity. House also has an irrigation system and a security system with four exterior cameras and each bedroom and the living room is wired for cable. This house has been well maintained and is more in ready.
